\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Ranking Event\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[General Cup]]<ref group=\"nb\">The event was called the General Cup International (2004/2005\u20132011/2012)</ref>\n|align=\"center\" colspan=\"13\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|A\n|align=\"center\" colspan=\"4\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|Tournament Not Held\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|NH\n|align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\"|A\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2012 General Cup|RR]]\n|style=\"text-align:center; background:#0f0;\"|[[2013 General Cup|'''W''']]\n|style=\"text-align:center; background:yellow;\"|[[2014 General Cup|SF]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2015 General Cup|RR]]\n|  colspan=\"30\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| Tournament Not Held\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[Snooker Shoot-Out|Shoot-Out]]\n| colspan=19 style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| Tournament Not Held\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2011 Snooker Shoot-Out|2R]]\n|style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2012 Snooker Shoot-Out|QF]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2013 Snooker Shoot-Out|2R]]\n|style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2014 Snooker Shoot-Out|QF]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2015 Snooker Shoot-Out|1R]]\n|align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|[[2016 Snooker Shoot-Out|1R]]\n| colspan=23 style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|Ranking Event\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:78%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! colspan=6|Performance Table Legend\n|-\n| align=\"center\" style=\"color:#cccccc;\" width=\"30\"|LQ\n| lost in the qualifying draw\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background:#afeeee;\"|#R\n| lost in the early rounds of the tournament<br />(WR = Wildcard round, RR = Round robin)\n| align=\"center\" style=\"